<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Sualnak lam zul-mi vialte hna, Bawipa nan zumh ahcun, Dinh-daihnak kha
 an pek hna lai, Mi nunnem ngai a si.

[C1]
   Zum cio tuah u, zum cio tuah u, Zum cio ko tuah u, An khamh hna lai,
   an khamh hna lai, A zummi vialte.

[V2]
 Bawi Jesuh cu thing cungah khan, Fahnak a in ca-ah, A thi in a tawlmi
 vialte, Hawhra nak an rang deuh.

[C2]
   Zum cio tuah u, zum cio tuah u, Zum cio ko tuah u, An khamh hna lai,
   an khamh hna lai, A zummi vialte.

[V3]
 Jesuh, lam le biatak a si, Dinhnak ram kalnak lam; Zungzal thluachuah
 a pek hna lai, Amah zummi vialte.

[C3]
   Zum cio tuah u, zum cio tuah u, Zum cio ko tuah u, An khamh hna lai,
   an khamh hna lai, A zummi vialte.

[V4]
 Ram tha zoh in kal tuah u law, A thiang bu vialte hna, Nun dongh lonak
 zungzal inn tha, Vancung kan Pa sinah,

[C4]
   Zum cio tuah u, zum cio tuah u, Zum cio ko tuah u, An khamh hna lai,
   an khamh hna lai, A zummi vialte.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
<title>ZUM KO TUAH U CH242</title>
<hymn_number>242</hymn_number>
</song>